<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
     <meta charset="UTF-8">
     <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
     <title>{{ subject }}</title>
     <style>
          body, table, td {
               margin: 0;
               padding: 0;
               font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
               background-color: #f3f5f8;
          }
          img {
               display: block;
               border: 0;
          }
          .container {
               max-width: 600px;
               margin: 0 auto;
               background: #ffffff;
               border-radius: 6px;
          }
          .header {
               padding: 20px;
               text-align: left;
               border-bottom: 4px solid {{ color_line_header }};
          }
          .header img {
               height: 26px;
          }
          .content {
               padding: 30px 40px;
               color: #080f1a;
               font-size: 16px;
               line-height: 24px;
          }
          .btn {
               display: inline-block;
               margin: 15px auto;
               padding: 12px 24px;
               font-size: 16px;
               color: {{ color_button_cta_text }};
               background-color: {{ color_button_cta_bg }};
               border-radius: 3px;
               text-decoration: none;
               text-align: center;
               width: 280px;
          }
          .footer {
               text-align: center;
               padding: 20px;
               font-size: 12px;
               color: {{ color_text_footer }};
          }
          @media (max-width: 600px) {
               .content {
                    padding: 20px;
               }
               .btn {
                    width:fit-content;
               }
          }
     </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
     <div class="header">
          <a href="https://www.hellohumans.fr/"><img src="{{ image_svg_header }}" alt="HelloHumans"></a>
     </div>
     <div class="content">
          <p>Bonjour l’équipe HelloHumans,</p>
          <p>Un nouvel incident a été signalé via l’application :</p>

          <table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px;">
               <!-- Utilisateur -->
               <tr>
                    <td style="background:#f0f4fa; padding:10px; border:1px solid #dde4ed; width:30%; font-weight:bold;">
                         Utilisateur
                    </td>
                    <td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #dde4ed;">
                         ID : {{ user_id }}
                         Nom : {{ user_name }}<br>
                         Email : {{ user_email }}<br>
                    </td>
               </tr>
               <!-- Appareil -->
               <tr>
                    <td style="background:#f0f4fa; padding:10px; border:1px solid #dde4ed; font-weight:bold;">
                         Appareil
                    </td>
                    <td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #dde4ed;">
                         {{ device_name }}
                    </td>
               </tr>
               <!-- Page -->
               <tr>
                    <td style="background:#f0f4fa; padding:10px; border:1px solid #dde4ed; font-weight:bold;">
                         Page
                    </td>
                    <td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #dde4ed;">
                         <a href="{{ page_url }}">{{ page_url }}</a>
                    </td>
               </tr>
               <!-- Détails du rapport -->
               <tr>
                    <td style="background:#f0f4fa; padding:10px; border:1px solid #dde4ed; font-weight:bold;">
                         Informations
                    </td>
                    <td style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #dde4ed;">
                         <strong>Type :</strong> {{ type }}<br>
                         <strong>Description :</strong><br>
                         {{ description }}
                    </td>
               </tr>
          </table>

          <p style="margin-top:20px;">
               Si une capture d’écran a été fournie, elle est jointe à cet email.<br>
               Merci de votre prise en charge rapide.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top:30px; font-style:italic;">L’équipe HelloHumans</p>
     </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
